## Working together
- **Remote:** {{REMOTE_INFO}}
- **Claim work in `DOCS/ROADMAP.md`** before starting an item (set Owner + branch, commit that first)
  so collaborators see it. Prefer feature branches; pull before you push.
- **Code change ⇒ doc change in the same commit:** new/renamed public symbol or file →
  `MODULE_MAP.md`; new behavior/quirk/dependency → `ARCHITECTURE.md`; any of the above → a
  `CHANGELOG.md` entry (newest first).
- `.claude/settings.json` (shared) holds the agreed permission allowlist; put personal overrides in
  `.claude/settings.local.json` (gitignored).
